        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Zack', 3: 'Fighting in isolation led to our crushing defeat, to Sophiasburgh\\'s ruin. And now, I see it plainly: humanity is poised to repeat the very same mistake.', 4: '1'}"
