        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Zack', 3: 'Wrong. This is precisely the problem that only world unification can solve. Human conflict springs from conflicting wills. But will is not innate; it is implanted in the mind by \"memetics\": societies, nations, ideologies.', 4: '1'}"
